This library defines all classes needed to implement Graphs and Algorithms for GraLog.

The main purpose of this library is to give a starting point for plugin-developers. There are two important packages in this library namely de.hu.gralog.graph and de.hu.gralog.graph.alg. The first one contains all classes needed to implement your own types of graphs the second one contains all classes needed to implement your own algorithms.
